org.ndnx.ndn.protocol
Class KeyLocator

java.lang.Object
  org.ndnx.ndn.impl.encoding.GenericXMLEncodable
      org.ndnx.ndn.protocol.KeyLocator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, XMLEncodable, ContentNameProvider
public class KeyLocator
extends GenericXMLEncodable
implements XMLEncodable, Serializable, ContentNameProvider, Cloneable

A KeyLocator specifies where a content consumer or intermediary can find the public key necessary to verify a piece of content. It might include the key itself, a certificate containing the key, or a NDN name pointing to a location where the key can be found.
